title: Book of Tales - Tales of the Arabian Nights
description:
This is a fan-created ebook conversion of the "Book of Tales" (300-page spiral-bound book) that is included with the 2009 Z-Man publication of the board game "Tales of the Arabian Nights."

It contains both epub and Mobi versions.

The ebook includes links to the various tales and clickable choices so that it is not necessary to use a separate Reaction Matrix to determine what story number to go to.

Some typos and grammatical errors from the original text have been corrected
